title: Enter At Your Own Risk
description:
Some places may just seem like a dot on a map, but all those dots are living, breathing spaces. Any entity that passes through somewhere leaves a piece of itself behind. Sometimes that energy is comforting. But other times it’s vengeful and leaves that place corrupted. So be careful and enter at your own risk.  

First, the true horror story of taunting footsteps 
Followed by a most deadly game
Then, dead lovers seek retribution 
Finally in our featured story, a tale of revenge you’ll be rooting for
